WEBVTT

00:12:28.400 --> 00:12:31.296
for that one which they know and love.

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:34.096
The children indeed are our future.

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:37.616
Let us please teach them
to love our feathermakers,

00:12:37.640 --> 00:12:39.576
because the love of birds

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:43.936
can be a huge gateway
to appreciating all forms of nature.

00:12:43.960 --> 00:12:45.176
Thank you very much.

00:12:45.200 --> 00:12:50.456
(Applause)

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:51.920
Thank you.